wild Spaniard
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(Aciphylla spp.) <i> wild </i> perhaps from analogy with wild Irishman
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:Spaniard, bloody Spaniard, giant Spaniard; cf. wild Irishman
